  <brief_title>Minimally Invasive Treatment Methods for Pilonidal Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Prospective Comparison of Crystallized Phenol and Platelet Rich Plasma Applications in Treatment of Pilonidal Sinus Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
