  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients with pilonidal sinus disease will be randomised to two groups (crystallised phenol
      and platelet rich plasma). Sinus healing time, patient satisfaction, complications and
      recurrence rates will be compared.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients with pilonidal sinus disease will be treated by either crystallised phenol or
      platelet rich plasma application. Treatment results, healing time, postprocedural
      complications, patient satisfaction and recurrences will be compared.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
